list.fullDescription:
Royal Battle is everything we love about Battle Royale games and more. You’ll be thrown into a world where you must survive and complete your objective. The real Hunger Games! Find what you need, navigate the terrain, and communicate with other participants - choose your strategy and win!

**Additional features:**  
 - Randomly generated worlds, from post-apocalypse to gothic fantasy;  
 - A serious challenge to compete with friends in a new way;  
 - Freedom of choice in strategy and tactics;  
 - Results, points, and achievements for each player at the end!
